                <head>333. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>The discussion at the White House recorded in the memorandum of conversation,
                        <ref target="#d332">
                        <hi rend="italic">supra,</hi>
                    </ref> next turned to the Middle East and China. A separate memorandum of
                    conversation is printed in volume XIII, pages 732–733. It was circulated to
                        <persName corresp="#p_WJH1">Whitney</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_MRD1"
                        >Murphy</persName>, <persName corresp="#p_RGF1">Reinhardt</persName>, SMITH,
                    and <persName corresp="#p_ECB1">Elbrick</persName> on October 25 as document MTW
                        <gloss target="#t_MC1">MC</gloss>–17.</p>
            </div>
